	<span class="anthracite size13" contentbodystyle="Anthracite">Before I forget, a note on this installment of the conclusion:

Chief's tip: When installing a monitoring application, install=
 from a command prompt=2E  Check disk space=2E  Leave workstation as=
 undisturbed as possible=2E  If all else fails, shut the=
 workstation down gently and simulate a power outage=2E  One of my=
 favorite tricks is to take out the batteries of a desk clock=
 that runs off of AC power so it resets and blinks "12:00"=2E  

I purposely did not include the other interviews I conducted in=
 previous postings=2E  There has to be some suspense=2E  :-)



 

