    </div>
	<span class="anthracite size13" contentbodystyle="Anthracite">Following up on a few comments:

- The 'ears' software installs just like many commercial monitoring applications.  It starts with every reboot, and can be automatically uninstalled by inserting the original CD and issuing a command with a password.

- I (like many TV dramas) add new clues through every posting.  If the events were obvious through every posting, what fun would it be to read?  And what incentive would I have to keep writing.  :-)

- CBK: What? This thing is long enough!  It could have been a book by itself.

