	<span class="anthracite size13" contentbodystyle="Anthracite">"Ears" is a semi-commercial monitoring application that I've used=
 on Windows machines=2E  It's very transparent to the untrained=
 eye=2E  It can be configured to capture keystrokes, specific=
 traffic types, etc=2E  It's nothing that you couldn't do a google=
 search for and find a plethora of options available=2E  We=
 nick-named it "ears" one day and it stuck=2E



